name: Genevieve_Double_Door_Floor_Cabinet_by_Elegant_Home_Fashions
reviews: This is a very nice cabinet for the price point. Easy to assemble and very sturdy.
Better than the picture! Works very good in my bathroom Purchased the floor cabinet to. Store all my Towels and bath mats in both the WALL and FLOOR cabinets
description: Keep your home organized with this Gevenieve double-door floor cabinet. This cabinet features two adjustable shelves that support up to 10 pounds each and provides ample storage space for items such as linens, clothing, books and bath supplies.
